'''Kaeth''' is an unseen character mentioned in the episode &quot;[[The Lion and the Rose]]&quot;. He is deceased when the events of the series begin and is not expected to appear in the series. He was a [[Grand Maester]] and the author of the book ''[[Lives of Four Kings]]''.
